      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ORGANISED KAOS (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (29.18) in a OPEN at this track. Solid record at the distance winning three races. The form out of last race has been strong. Should bounce back. GUS THE GREAT (4) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 2.75 lengths at Rockhampton in a handy 24.01 beating Feisty Fawny. Has a win and three minor placings from four starts from this draw. Has definite claims. MIZUKI HEART (7) has shown good improvement at her last two starts, the latest scoring at this track over 380m. Expected to feature again. BARNSLEY (2) placed two runs ago then again in the money last time when second (29.27) at this track in a Restricted WIN.",
